{"id":4716,"date":"2025-07-25T13:12:46","date_gmt":"2025-07-25T13:12:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/beanhiredev.com\/?post_type=product_update&#038;p=4716"},"modified":"2025-07-25T13:12:46","modified_gmt":"2025-07-25T13:12:46","slug":"seamless-integration-with-zoom-ms-teams","status":"publish","type":"product_update","link":"https:\/\/oorwin.ai\/product-updates\/seamless-integration-with-zoom-ms-teams\/","title":{"rendered":"Seamless Integration with Zoom &amp; MS Teams"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Overview<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019re excited to roll out native integrations with <strong>Zoom<\/strong> and <strong>Microsoft Teams<\/strong>, enabling recruiters and hiring managers to <strong>schedule, join, and manage interviews<\/strong> directly from hrumbles\u2014without switching platforms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>What\u2019s New<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>\ud83d\udd17 <strong>One-Click Interview Scheduling:<\/strong> Add Zoom or Teams links automatically when setting up interviews in hrumbles.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>\ud83d\udcc5 <strong>Calendar Sync:<\/strong> Ensure meeting details, participants, and links are auto-synced with Google Calendar or Outlook.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f <strong>Smart Rescheduling:<\/strong> Need to move an interview? The integration updates everything in real-time across tools.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>\ud83e\uddfe <strong>Recording &amp; Notes Ready:<\/strong> Post-interview, access recordings (if enabled) and attach evaluation notes in the same interface.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Why It Matters<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>No more copying links or toggling between platforms. With these integrations, you streamline interview workflows, reduce scheduling errors, and <strong>deliver a more professional experience for candidates and interviewers alike<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">